// Device Authorization Grant API for the Hades schema registry.
//
// Implements the OAuth 2.0 Device Authorization Grant (RFC 8628). This flow
// is designed for devices that cannot open a browser (e.g. the buf CLI, CI
// runners). The device requests a code, displays the user_code to the operator,
// and polls PollDeviceToken until the user approves the grant in a browser
// session via ApproveDeviceGrant.

